it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface AppModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface AppModule
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'App Module'. Modulo dell'applicativo. Da mantenere in un file separato.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Content Panels
    • Ext Security Model
    • Secure
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getAppModule()
